id.description: The unique identifier of the satisfaction rating entry.

survey_id.description: The unique identifier of the survey associated with the satisfaction rating.

user_id.description: The unique identifier of the user who provided the satisfaction rating.

agent_id.description: The unique identifier of the agent who received the satisfaction rating.

feedback.description: The feedback provided by the user for the interaction with the agent.

group_id.description: The unique identifier of the group to which the agent belongs.

ticket_id.description: The unique identifier of the ticket related to the satisfaction rating.

created_at.description: The timestamp when the satisfaction rating was created.

updated_at.description: The timestamp when the satisfaction rating was last updated.

ratings.description: The ratings provided by the user to indicate satisfaction level.
